---
title: Quick Beef & Mushroom Linguine with Garlic Pangrattato & Apple Salad
description: We’ve livened up a classic pasta dish with flavourful beef mince, tender mushrooms and our much-loved garlic & herb seasoning.
You’re going to impress even your toughest critic with this gorgeous offering.

*Keep an eye out...Due to recent sourcing challenges, we’ve replaced fettuccine with linguine, which may be a little different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
